  7) onna no hito wa se ga takai desu ka? = woman tall? = hai, se ga takai desu = yes, tall
  8) otoko no hito wa se ga hikui desu ka? = boy short? = hai, se hikui desu = yes, short
  9) onna no hito wa kami ga nagai desu ka? = woman long hair? = hai, kami ga nagai desu = yes, long hair
  10) otoko no hito wa me ga chiisai desu ka? = boy small eyes? = iie, me ga ooki desu = no, big eyes
